{
  "stem": "1775.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 156.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And my husband went down to get his father to come up there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They were all gone from there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The Germans find the hiding place and they took him.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And that's the last time I saw my husband's father and his uncles and his brothers.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "That's when they went away to Majdanek.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "My brother, when he came back, he told me he saw them in Majdanek.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "That's where they were.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And we were there a whole week.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Then we came back to the ghetto again because there was no other place where to go.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So we went back to the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And when we went back to the ghetto, I saw I lost most of my family.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And we started to work again by sorting clothing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "That was the first thing they needed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Because after so many people left, there was so much, you know, stuff left.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "So they took us there to sort the clothes.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "So I was working there for a while.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "This was-- this was May, the beginning of May.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Three weeks later, they round up the rest of the people.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And again, we're going.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And this time, I wasn't so fortunate.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "I got put in in the train backs, just like the other people, with my husband, my cousin and his wife, and another cousin of mine.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] It was-- they undressed us almost naked.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "So they-- so we couldn't hide anythings.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And they didn't want us to jump from the trains.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "Because when you have clothes and you jump from the train, it's easier for you to get away.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "But since they undressed us, we couldn't run away.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "I-- at that-- at that time, I think I gave up.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "I didn't-- I couldn't take it anymore.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "I said, that's it.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
